Then push both changes to GitHub. Render will redeploy automatically.

---

## Step 2 — Fix Render's Build & Start settings

Go to your Render dashboard → your mock server service → **Settings**.

- **Build Command:** `npm install && npm run build`
- **Start Command:** `npm start`

Save and redeploy.

---

## Step 3 — Fix the MOCK LP row in Supabase

Go to [supabase.com](https://supabase.com) → your project → **Table Editor** → table `lp_counterparties`.

Find the row where `lp_secret_id = MOCK`. Edit the `direct_ws_url` column and set it to:
```
wss://YOUR-RENDER-URL.onrender.com/ws/v1
